{"id":2580,"date":"2023-05-24T15:24:20","date_gmt":"2023-05-24T08:24:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2580"},"modified":"2023-09-18T15:26:03","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T08:26:03","slug":"giang-vien-nganh-luat-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-xin-the-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/giang-vien-nganh-luat-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-xin-the-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"GI\u1ea2NG VI\u00caN NG\u00c0NH LU\u1eacT &#8211; TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4 \u201cX\u1ecaN\u201d TH\u1ebe N\u00c0O ???"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean &#8220;c\u1ef1c x\u1ecbn&#8221;. L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean t\u1eeb ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi theo h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4, gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean s\u1ebd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt, th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n ph\u00e1p l\u00fd, v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c x\u1eed l\u00fd nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e1p l\u00fd \u0111\u1eb7t ra trong th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n.<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc 50% l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft v\u00e0 50% th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng tranh lu\u1eadn, t\u01b0 duy ph\u1ea3n bi\u1ec7n,&#8230; qua c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ngay t\u1eeb khi v\u00e0o Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia CLB v\u0103n h\u00f3a Lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i giao l\u01b0u v\u0103n h\u00f3a, v\u0103n ngh\u1ec7, th\u1ec3 thao, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">100% Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, c\u00f4ng ty Lu\u1eadt, v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eefng v\u1ec1 l\u00fd lu\u1eadn, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t cho sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean Khoa Lu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 qua c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15648\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15650\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/z4368562073874_45bb937fbe3d05febd889f6f6f0c4175-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15646\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke2-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15642\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke5-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15638\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke6-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15640\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke7-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-15636\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/Tke8-01-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" \/><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean &#8220;c\u1ef1c x\u1ecbn&#8221;. L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 va